{
  "3047820": {
    "name": "僵尸街区：涂鸦特工队",
    "steam_appid": 3047820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群来自街区的变异少年是人类在这个充满色彩与幽默的僵尸末日中最后的希望。用荒唐的武器轰炸怪诞僵尸，在城市中狂野涂鸦，并在每个任务的结尾对抗可怕的僵尸头目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小队中的每位英雄都拥有独特的玩法风格：选择你的角色，从垃圾桶中翻出最奇怪的枪，欣赏那些疯狂的爆头动画。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/29204baaecf2c3812c6666a7c2fd1adb.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/7963cb4b1ef69f1836ba11afbfd89cf0.poster.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/7963cb4b1ef69f1836ba11afbfd89cf0.webm?t=1772225392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四位拥有各自能力与战斗风格的年轻变异者，准备好炸翻一切僵尸！选出你最喜欢的那一个（或者造型最酷的），疯狂出击吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/d151d99bf9f00a528cf69db0e817abcc.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=78 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/d14465ac72969a95cc467e9c49a4490f.poster.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/d14465ac72969a95cc467e9c49a4490f.webm?t=1772225392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >番茄酱喷射器、泡泡糖发射枪、鲨鱼头霰弹枪，甚至是女巫的扫帚……用各种疯狂的武器打到僵尸怀疑人生（也可能是“尸生”）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/8ebf84517eec33234e9b5028d3cf35bb.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/bc089b670e8f7d586bccb22c3dc4a371.poster.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/bc089b670e8f7d586bccb22c3dc4a371.webm?t=1772225392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的游戏策划完全疯了。准备好迎接可爱狗狗僵尸、触手胖僵尸、肌肉警察僵尸，甚至是穿着内裤的科学怪人。虽然毫无逻辑，但绝对爆笑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/6de8b9a4da86813eb644fce77ecd7e62.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/0727dec83ca354d295011daf2ea843e8.poster.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/0727dec83ca354d295011daf2ea843e8.webm?t=1772225392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在僵尸末日中喷涂涂鸦可不是件容易的事。每次你尝试涂墙，都可能召唤一大群尸潮。艺术从未如此危险（也从未如此多彩）！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/a43ffec5995875b1950c2399d4810a99.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/9df68d9bef3dfc604042f2e20a12b425.poster.avif?t=1772225392\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047820/extras/9df68d9bef3dfc604042f2e20a12b425.webm?t=1772225392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个僵尸明显和别人不一样。它更强、更狠，而且每次复活都变得更强。打败这个Boss僵尸，告诉它谁才是真正的怪物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
